# Server rules

Applies to: `server/**`

Read `BACKEND_PLAN.md` before making changes.

Implement only the next unfinished task.

Explain the plan before writing code.

Keep views thin.

Business logic belongs in `services.py`.

Use Django ORM and PostgreSQL.

Do not modify unrelated files.

After coding:
- Explain what changed.
- Tell me which commands to run.
- Suggest only the next task.
